  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Specific Aims:  1) Measure exhalation enthalpy in patients receiving conventional positive
      pressure ventilation during stable hemodynamic conditions. 2) Measure exhalation enthalpy in
      patients following change from two-lung ventilation to one-lung ventilation while minute
      ventilation remains constant.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
